FBIS3-56956 "drsov014_r_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-014 Document Type:Daily Report 21 Jan 1994 Azerbaijan Gasanov Turns Down Secretary of State Post LD2001064094 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 0500 GMT 20 Jan 94 LD2001064094 Moscow Mayak Radio Network Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Text] Gasan Gasanov, minister of foreign affairs of Azerbaijan, has refused the offer of the post of the republic's secretary of state. An ANI correspondent has learned this from sources close to the government. At the same time, in the circles of the secretary of state it is reported that Gaydar Aliyev intends to eliminate that post in general and introduce a new post, that of vice president.
